cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.AI

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with Spoken Language Understanding (SLU) and its design for small devices. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is also a likely category as the paper deals with speech recognition and understanding. 
- cs.LG (Learning) is another possible category as the paper discusses the performance of the SLU system and its comparison with cloud-based commercial solutions. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possible category as the paper deals with the design of an embedded system for SLU. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with natural language processing and understanding.
